Class Movie

java.lang.Object
  org.rhwlab.snight.Movie
public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object

a class to emulate a Movie_t struct in StarryNight
In the June 2006 modifications the role for this object was reduced, but it was retained to avoid unnecessary changes elsewhere in the code. At this point, only the xy_res and z_res parameters are in use, and they are being handled via the AceTree configuration file
